---
title: Sausages with Spinach Colcannon in a rich onion gravy
description: Colcannon is about as classic an Irish dish as they come. It's fitting then that in this recipe it's served alongside another Irish favourite: succulent pork sausages. Topped with rich onion gravy, this might just be the ultimate comfort meal.
